file.name: swagger.yaml
file.content:
openapi: 3.0.2
info:
  title: Test
  version: 0.0.0
servers:
  - url: https://example.com/rest/v1
paths:
  /users:
    get:
      operationId: getUsers
      summary: List all users
      description: |
        Foo bar
      tags:
        - Users
      parameters:
        - $ref: '#/components/parameters/userState'
      responses:
        '200':
          $ref: '#/components/responses/UserList'
components:
  parameters:
    userState:
      in: query
      name: userState
      required: true
      description: "User state"
      schema:
        $ref: "#/components/schemas/userState"
  schemas:
    userNames:
      type: string
      description: username
      example: 'User name'
    userState:
      type: string
      enum:
        - ACTIVE
        - BOTH
        - INACTIVE
      description: User state
      example: ACTIVE
  responses:
    UserList:
      description: Return the response of user names.
      content:
        application/json:
          schema:
            type: array
            items:
              $ref: '#/components/schemas/userNames'
